    "Rogue Trader Dynasty Personae - Distinguishing Feature": {
      "name": "Rogue Trader Dynasty Personae - Distinguishing Feature",
      "description": "<p>Distinguishing Feature</p>",
      "results": {
        "1-1": "The Dynasty’s coat of arms tattooed on their face.",
        "2-2": "A shoddy copy of their Dynasty’s Warrant of Trade is proudly pinned to their hat.",
        "3-3": "Their hair is ostentatiously styled, sporting several expensive adornments.",
        "4-4": "They wear a golden mask depicting their family’s founder.",
        "5-5": "They wear several heavy rings on each finger, which clink at every movement.",
        "6-6": "Followed by a gold-plated Servo-Skull holding a tray with refreshments.",
        "7-7": "Unsettling look in their eyes, looks haunted by the things they’ve seen.",
        "8-8": "They are preceded by cherubic servitors spreading incense.",
